history.content:
At Girls Teaching Girls to Code (GTC), we empower college girls pursuing Computer Science and Engineering to connect with local high school girls and inspire them through mentorship and applied projects. Throughout the school year, we host events to extend the influence of women in technology and inspire young girls to pursue their interests in tech. We hope that you find the mission inspiring and invite you to join us in empowering women in tech! :) 

 

We will have our info session on Wednesday, Feb 3rd, 8-9PM PST. 

Click “interested” to remain updated on recruitment info: https://fb.me/e/2UK54X0F5 

To learn more about GTC: https://www.girlsteachinggirlstocode.org/ 

 

**We are currently recruiting for General Members and Project Leads**
General Members Application (Due 2/14): https://tinyurl.com/gtcsp2021 

Project Lead Application (Due 2/9): https://tinyurl.com/gtcproject
